      "updated": 1741615000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Technical summary:\n1. UI calls /ensure to match or create an agent.\n2. Registry uses meta-agent generation when no fit exists.\n3. Agent, versions, and reflection events persist to SQLite + JSONL history.\n4. /run executes the selected agent, evaluates output, refines if needed, and returns final answer plus diagnostics.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Technical summary:\n1. UI calls /ensure to match or create an agent.\n2. Registry uses meta-agent generation when no fit exists.\n3. Agent, versions, and reflection events persist to SQLite + JSONL history.\n4. /run executes the selected agent, evaluates output, refines if needed, and returns final answer plus diagnostics.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
